{"tid":1787862,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"譚杏藍搞生日P被投訴聲浪大　發文道歉被批「無腦兼白癡」","createTime":"2019-12-18T08:43:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T08:50:56.000Z","uid":165934,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"512256d47fae68d261d01d2787b59f9e38280c96","tid":1787862,"uid":165934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T08:43:49.000Z","msg":"歌手譚杏藍 (小花) 今日 (16/12)30歲生日，日前就與一眾好朋友預先舉行生日會慶祝。好友聚首一堂本是好開心事，但日前小花未有在Instagram內分享開心合照，而是貼上一則道歉長文，向因為是次生日會受到困擾的人士致最深的道歉！<br />\n<br />\n小花有交代事件始末，指當日在朋友的工廠大廈的露台 ( 同時設小舞台)舉行生日會，由於明白工廠大廈附近也有民居地方，所以本來已決定於11時後把全場音量調低。不過場內的朋友有醉酒又過份興奮地唱歌，在11時多就有警察到場了解投訴事件。小花最後又再次道歉，認為事件為她再次上了寶貴的一課！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d4iErvE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd4iErvE.png&h=780efb0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小花在文中多次提到「朋友」，又指自己對於警察上門一事是後知後覺......就惹來不少網民批評她是不負責任、不知所謂！小花自己都有回應到部份的留言......<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ctTkVpd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FctTkVpd.jpg&h=83cfe3ac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8258c6cc936e80af7af5d90d39fad5f7b768dce2","tid":1787862,"uid":165934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T08:44:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mnsefpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmnsefpw.jpg&h=6214db51&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b8eb269e814ea01b8b993fb95c67261709519e19","tid":1787862,"uid":165934,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T08:45:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JyRuOKG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJyRuOKG.jpg&h=b44adfff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27fbb2c0a90d192c966db023fccc875298268073","tid":1787862,"uid":165934,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T08:45:29.000Z","msg":"大家又接受她的回應嗎？"},{"pid":"94643e39e2f471220137b3932945f0026ac1071f","tid":1787862,"uid":83557,"like":0,"